data.description: ** Assumable VA loan at 2.49%! ** Lovingly maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts a 3 car garage and captivating curb appeal with its well-manicured landscaping. As you step through the front entryway, you are greeted by coffered ceilings that seamlessly extend into the home office, setting the tone for the features within. The open floorplan bathes the interior in natural light, accentuated by soaring ceilings, and crown molding throughout that create an elegant and inviting atmosphere. The stunning kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, 42-inch cabinets offering ample storage, and a convenient center island that doubles as a breakfast bar. Adjacent to the kitchen is the formal dining room, providing easy access for seamless entertaining. The spacious great room features a wall-sized slider that not only invites the outdoors in but also extends the living space onto a covered and screened-in patio. The bedrooms, generously sized, are split for privacy and offer plenty of living space. The primary bedroom stands out with its coffered and trey ceilings, walk-in closets, and an ensuite bathroom complete with a dual sink vanity and walk in shower. The backyard is fully fenced for added privacy and there are no rear neighbors. The Triple Creek community offers a wealth of amenities to enhance your lifestyle. The Club Amenity Center includes a Multi-Purpose Room and an Open-Air Social Room with an Expansive Pavilion, perfect for gatherings and events. There are two Resort-Style Pools, including a lap lane pool, a Splash Pad, a state-of-the-art Fitness Center, a Tot Lot, and even an Open Playfield for outdoor fun. Sports enthusiasts will appreciate the Tennis Courts and Basketball Court, while pet owners will love the Central Bark Dog Park. Community Trails wind through the area, providing opportunities for walking, jogging, and biking. Come see this home today!
